N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 1.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

As used herein, the following terms shall have the
following meanings: (a) Commissioner
means the Commissioner of Agriculture and Markets of the State of New

York. (b) Person means individual, partnership, corporation or cooperative association. (c) Vitamin D Milk means milk in which the
vitamin D content has been increased in the manner set forth in section
1.4
of this Part. (d) Approved laboratory means a laboratory
approved by the commissioner pursuant to section
1.2
of this Part. Notes
